# v1  Script Version
## Key
- Implemented basic chat functionality of the campus club AI assistant using pure function-based coding
- Completed the core workflow of Streamlit UI construction and LLM API calling
- Supported loading preset knowledge base content for Q&A

## Limitations
- Messy code structure with poor reusability
- No exception handling, program crashes directly when API call fails
- Knowledge base is hard-coded in the code, making modifications inconvenient
- Low code readability, not conducive to subsequent iterations

## Usage
1. Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
2. Configure your LLM API key in the code
3. Run the project: streamlit run app_v1.py
